cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language understanding and text summarization, which are closely related to the fields of computational linguistics (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of Abstract Meaning Representation (AMR) also suggests a possible connection to information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.NE).
